nodes.title: CLIP Text Encode (Positive Prompt)
widgets_values:
Camera:
The camera begins low to the ground inside the fog-covered German forest. Soft push-forward dolly. Branches slide past the edges of frame. At second 3, a faint clearing opens. The camera continues forward, never morphing, only traversing physical terrain. At second 7 the ruined village slowly emerges through drifting smoke. Camera glides directly into the street and settles facing the abandoned houses at the final frame. One continuous forward movement, no loop.

nodes.title: CLIP Text Encode (Positive Prompt)
widgets_values:
Camera:
The shot opens very close to the cracked mossy gravestone. Slow rising crane-up moves over the stone into the foggy cemetery. At second 3 the camera drifts forward into open land. Terrain becomes barren and windy. At second 7 the camera clears the last trees and reveals the dead field landscape under heavy clouds. One smooth expansion of space.

nodes.title: CLIP Text Encode (Positive Prompt)
widgets_values:
Camera:
Camera slides forward along the wet cobblestone street, puddles reflecting fog. Subtle handheld sway. At second 4 the buildings thin and the camera continues down toward a river. The destroyed bridge appears through haze as the camera slowly ascends and tilts forward, ending centered on the collapsed arches. Pure spatial movement.

nodes.title: CLIP Text Encode (Positive Prompt)
widgets_values:
Camera:
Starts between rusted pipes and brick ruins. Camera pushes forward between debris. At second 4 it passes through an opening in the yard and enters a foggy plain. Railway tracks fade into visibility. Camera aligns with the tracks and glides forward along them into the distance. No morphing.

nodes.title: CLIP Text Encode (Positive Prompt)
widgets_values:
Camera:
Camera begins circling the cracked stone bird statue, slow clockwise orbit. At second 3 it leaves the orbit and travels forward across rocky ground. The ancient monument slowly rises through swirling clouds. Camera centers on it as mist curls around the stones. Continuous dolly.

nodes.title: CLIP Text Encode (Positive Prompt)
widgets_values:
Camera:
Shot opens upward into the sky with circling crows, camera drifting forward under the storm. As the camera lowers gently toward the landscape, broken architecture becomes visible. At second 6 the collapsed church emerges from fog. Camera ends advancing toward the fallen tower.

nodes.title: CLIP Text Encode (Positive Prompt)
widgets_values:
Camera:
Camera starts inside the broken doorway, pushing forward into the ruined room. Debris passes beneath frame. At second 3 the camera moves outside, revealing streets covered in ash. Drifting forward, glowing embers appear. The shot ends centered on the smoking rubble. No dissolve.

nodes.title: CLIP Text Encode (Positive Prompt)
widgets_values:
Camera:
Camera sweeps forward through jagged fog-covered peaks. Slow altitude drop. At second 4 the hillside becomes visible below. Camera descends toward a dark tunnel portal and glides into the fog at its entrance, stopping at the threshold. Smooth spatial transition.

nodes.title: CLIP Text Encode (Positive Prompt)
widgets_values:
Camera:
Starts moving between rusted tanks, pushing slowly through ground fog. The camera climbs a slight incline and transitions into open terrain. At second 6 the old road with flickering lamps appears. The camera aligns with the road and follows it straight into deep fog.

nodes.title: CLIP Text Encode (Positive Prompt)
widgets_values:
Camera:
Close pass of corroded bronze statues, camera pushing through overgrown vines. At second 3 it enters a stone corridor. The destroyed stone reliefs appear ahead, illuminated by diffused fog. Camera moves right up to the cracked surface. Continuous forward path.

nodes.title: CLIP Text Encode (Positive Prompt)
widgets_values:
Camera:
Wind tears through forest, camera advancing between bending trees. At second 4 the foliage parts and the landscape opens. Camera climbs a slow incline toward the distant destroyed castle. Ends facing the collapsing walls, valley fog rolling underneath. at the final frame. One continuous forward movement, no loop.

nodes.title: CLIP Text Encode (Positive Prompt)
widgets_values:
Camera:
Begins beside the rusted military vehicle, sliding forward past its hull. Camera moves through mud toward a rising slope. At second 6 the bunker entrance emerges. Camera settles directly in front of the concrete doorway.

nodes.title: CLIP Text Encode (Positive Prompt)
widgets_values:
Camera:
Camera follows the foggy rural road straight ahead, faint tree silhouettes on both sides. At second 5 terrain transitions into industrial wasteland. Fallen chimneys and steel frames rise. Camera ends moving toward the ruins in heavy haze.

nodes.title: CLIP Text Encode (Positive Prompt)
widgets_values:
Camera:
Starts extremely close on the cracked bell metal. Slow pull-back reveals the abandoned interior. Camera transitions outside into open fields. Broken wind turbines loom through fog. Camera glides toward them as clouds drift across frame.

nodes.title: CLIP Text Encode (Positive Prompt)
widgets_values:
Camera:
Camera pushes forward through debris of the fallen tower. At second 4 it enters overgrown terrain. The abandoned barracks emerge in frame. Camera centers on the empty courtyard as grass sways in wind.

nodes.title: CLIP Text Encode (Positive Prompt)
widgets_values:
Camera:
Camera slides past barbed wire strands in extreme close-up, then rises and moves forward into the clearing. At second 5 the mortuary building forms in silhouette. Camera approaches the stone facade in steady forward movement.

nodes.title: CLIP Text Encode (Positive Prompt)
widgets_values:
Camera:
Camera travels along wet train tracks, reflections shaking slightly with rain. At second 4 the mouth of a foggy tunnel appears. Camera rides straight into it, slowing as a faint figure silhouette becomes visible.

nodes.title: CLIP Text Encode (Positive Prompt)
widgets_values:
Camera:
Camera begins close on the burning torch; slow orbit. Then it advances through the forest, following the light spill. At second 6 a stone wall appears. Camera moves directly toward the rusted metal symbol illuminated by flickering shadows.

nodes.title: CLIP Text Encode (Positive Prompt)
widgets_values:

Camera glides across cracked pavement of the empty village square. At second 4 wind intensifies and dust sweeps past the camera. Broken ruins appear ahead. Camera ends facing torn cloth blowing violently in the wind.

nodes.title: CLIP Text Encode (Positive Prompt)
widgets_values:

Camera pushes through the broken wooden door into darkness. At second 3 it enters the ruined interior, scanning collapsed beams and burned walls. Ends advancing deeper into charred space.

nodes.title: CLIP Text Encode (Positive Prompt)

nodes.title: CLIP Text Encode (Positive Prompt)
widgets_values:

widgets_values:
